so, 
Workflow = a defined set of states + allowed transitions + who can perform them.
or
Workflow = States + Actions + Transitions + Roles.


How to create : 
1. Search WorkFLow List -> New - > Fille fields like name & doctype name
2. now you can add different states for the doctype
3. now you can add different Action/Transition Rules for the Doctype.



